Net-Pachube version 0.01
========================

This module provides a simple API for manipulating feeds on the
Pachube service (http://www.pachube.com/).  Currently it supports
updating a feed with a PUT request, fetching latest information
for a feed with a GET request and creating a new feed with a POST
request.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP
  XML::Simple

